               a) Bodmelqart ben Bodmelqart Tabahpi Griq.1 (Graeculus ?), <title>Neo-Punic</title> 28 from the door(s) of the Tiberian Temple of Rome and Augustus in the Forum Vetus.
               b) Iddibal Magonis f. Tapapius, <ref type="inscription" n="IRT0273">273</ref> (CE 42- 3),
               c) Ithymbal Arinis f. Sabinus Tapapius. <ref type="inscription" n="IRT0341">341</ref> (CE 61- 2); also in <title>Neo-Puni</title>c 29 (not dated), 
