               d) Abdemelqart Tabahpi, <title>Neo-Punic</title> 12, 1. (not dated). 
               [e) ...] Arinis f. Tapafius Diodorus Nizaz. <ref type="inscription" n="IRT0745">745</ref> (not dated). --> </p>
